The paper discusses the use of machine learning models such as autoencoder neural networks, principal components, and support vector regression for data imputation. These models are commonly used in the fields of machine learning (cs.LG), artificial intelligence (cs.AI), data science (cs.DS), neural networks (cs.NE), and computer vision (cs.CV). Therefore, these are the most likely arXiv CS sub-categories for this paper.
